  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<android.preference.Preference>

    public class PanSwitchPreference
extends android.preference.SwitchPreference
    A Preference that provides checkbox widget functionality specifically geared towards plugin developers.

    This preference will store a boolean into the SharedPreferences.
